snippet.textDisplay: Pakistan Coke Studio is thriving because it operates free from political influence and the control of the Pakistani establishment, which has negatively impacted many institutions in the country. This platform celebrates talented artists of all nationalities, languages, and cultures. Our nation should recognize the model Zulfi is building, characterized by honesty, hard work, merit-based opportunities, and a pure showcase of Pakistan's creative talent to the world. I'm particularly excited to see an Indian Gujarati from Norway contributing to this amazing project, and I thoroughly enjoyed his performance alongside artists like Kafi Khalil. Pakistan Zindabaad!
